                <h1>Discover Windows 10 Default Wallpaper Location</h1>
                <p>The default wallpaper for Windows 10 can be found in the following directory: C:\Windows\Web\Wallpaper. This folder contains various background images used by the operating system, including the default lock screen and desktop wallpaper options. Users can access and change these images for a more personalized desktop experience.</p>
